<section class="bg-gradient p-5 mb-5 banner resources-banner">
    <div class="wrapper">
        <div class="row flex-column flex-md-row justify-content-md-between align-items-md-center flex-container">
            <div class="col col-left">
                <h1 class="fw-bolder lh-1">Garden Starter Guide</h1>
                <p class="mt-3">Here you'll find useful information about how to plant, grow, and care for your crops.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="col d-flex justify-content-center justify-content-md-end align-items-start right-col">
                <img src="~/images/starter-guide-img.png" />
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>
<section class="[ row justify-content-center mx-0 g-2 position-relative pb-4 ] [ blog-posts ]">
    <div class="blogposts-container">
        <div class="[ row flex-column gap-4 flex-lg-row ] [ row-bottom ]">
            <div class="[ col bg-white ] [ article-col ]">
                <div class="[ row flex-column ] [ blog-post ]">
                    <div class="[ col ] [ text-container ]">
                        <h3 class="mt-3">Choosing a Location</h3>
                        <p>
                            The first step in starting a garden is choosing the right location. Your garden should be in a sunny spot with well-drained soil. It should also be close to a water source.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                    <a class="[ text-white fw-bold text-decoration-none btn py-2 px-4 mt-auto ] [ btn-link ]" asp-area="" asp-controller="" asp-action="">Learn More</a>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="[ col bg-white ] [ article-col ]">
                <div class="[ row flex-column ] [ blog-post ]">
                    <div class="[ col ] [ text-container ]">
                        <h3 class="mt-3">Planning Your Garden</h3>
                        <p>Once you've chosen a location, it's time to start planning your garden. Decide what crops you want to grow and how much space you need for each one. You can use a garden planner to help you lay out your garden.</p>

                    </div>
                    <a class="[ text-white fw-bold text-decoration-none btn py-2 px-4 mt-auto ] [ btn-link ]" asp-area="" asp-controller="" asp-action="">Learn More</a>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="[ col bg-white ] [ article-col ]">
                <div class="[ row flex-column ] [ blog-post ]">
                    <div class="[ col ] [ text-container ]">
                        <h3 class="mt-3">Planting your Crops</h3>
                        <p>When you're ready to plant your crops, be sure to follow the instructions on the seed packet. Plant your seeds at the proper depth and spacing. Water your seeds regularly and keep the soil moist.</p>

                    </div>
                    <a class="[ text-white fw-bold text-decoration-none btn py-2 px-4 mt-auto ] [ btn-link ]" asp-area="" asp-controller="" asp-action="">Learn More</a>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="[ col bg-white ] [ article-col ]">
                <div class="[ row flex-column ] [ blog-post ]">
                    <div class="[ col ] [ text-container ]">
                        <h3 class="mt-3">Maintaining Your Garden</h3>
                        <p>When you're ready to plant your crops, be sure to follow the instructions on the seed packet. Plant your seeds at the proper depth and spacing. Water your seeds regularly and keep the soil moist.</p>

                    </div>
                    <a class="[ text-white fw-bold text-decoration-none btn py-2 px-4 mt-auto ] [ btn-link ]" asp-area="" asp-controller="Home" asp-action="ManageGarden">Learn More</a>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="[ col bg-white ] [ article-col ]">
                <div class="[ row flex-column ] [ blog-post ]">
                    <div class="[ col ] [ text-container ]">
                        <h3 class="mt-3">Harvesting your Crops</h3>
                        <p>When your crops are ripe, it's time to harvest them. Be sure to harvest your crops at the right time to ensure the best flavor and quality.</p>
                    </div>
                    <a class="[ text-white fw-bold text-decoration-none btn py-2 px-4 mt-auto ] [ btn-link ]" asp-area="" asp-controller="" asp-action="">Learn More</a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="additional-resources mt-5 text-center">
            <h4>Additional Resources</h4>
            <p>Here are some additional resources that you may find helpful:</p>
            <ul class="p-0 resourceList">
                <li><a href="https://www.almanac.com/gardening">The Old Farmer's Almanac</a></li>
                <li><a href="https://garden.org/">The National Gardening Association</a></li>
                <li><a href="https://www.ahs.org/">The American Horticultural Society</a></li>
            </ul>
        </div>
      
    </div>
</section>

